<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink303">
<l>putukkalat taṉṉa kaṉiya vālam</l>
<l>pōkiṟaṉait taṭukkum vēṉi laruñcuran</l>
<l>taṇṇiya viṉiya vāka</l>
<l>vemmoṭuñ ceṉmō viṭalai nīyē</l>
      </lg>
  <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O young man! You should go [together] with us to that the harsh desert,</l>
<l>where summer heat prevents birds from leaving </l>
<l>the Banyan tree, whose ripe fruit are like new claypots, </l>
<l>turn into cool and pleasant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
